Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:35.70,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只会有一辆电车经过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:38.83,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那是又可爱又令人留恋的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.43,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是和谈恋爱一样了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.49,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然互相注意着对方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:46.80,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有互相接近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:48.50,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.95,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 某天他突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:53.65,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:56.93,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要回复
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:59.94,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你明白我的心意就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:05.71,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在自己被告之「不需要回复」之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.50,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法做出回应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:10.37,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心意就被丢在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:16.84,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:18.84,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:22.70,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个站姿 用手拿书的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.06,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个时候一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.46,0:01:25.62,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:28.23,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雪子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:30.61,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:33.39,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「雪子小姐」是我随便起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:35.06,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:37.18,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我看上去很奇怪 但我不是什么可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.03,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会有那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.12,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:42.74,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那封信…是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.56,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您是齐木先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.06,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.77,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为信封上有写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:58.19,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这封信是我在整理妈妈的行李时找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.67,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？ 那个…也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:03.40,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说 你是那个人的女儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:04.45,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.25,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈是个写作家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:10.19,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她把学生时代的回忆留在了随笔上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.22,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这些随笔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:15.08,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就把书和信都拿了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.50,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,重温妈妈的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:19.20,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就有了这次的偶遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.96,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是妈妈让我们相遇的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:26.59,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她…写了在这里的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.48,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您要读读吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:32.95,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:34.55,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.36,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:40.65,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻时候的我太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:45.44,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原来明明有戏的 而我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:49.45,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,齐木先生是真心喜欢我妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:54.18,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 看着和妈妈长得一样的我 会心动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:58.36,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不…已经这把年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.81,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对女高中生心动是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.32,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉回答得有些敷衍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.04,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的年轻人都这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.99,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈也是这种感觉的女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:09.01,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:12.40,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 那过去未能实现的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.98,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又带来了新的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.76,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这份相遇 今后会怎样发展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.77,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,发展…发展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.33,Fumikiri_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不不…年龄差距这么大
